result.name: 2011-natural-england-north-west-region-european-marine-sites-condition-monitoring-of-littoral-f
result.notes: A Natural England commissioned intertidal survey conducted by the Centre for Marine and Coastal Studies (CMACS). The aim of the survey was to provide a baseline dataset for future management and condition monitoring of the intertidal interest features in the Dee Estuary. Phase I Biotope Mapping including sediment cores for fauna and Particle Size Analysis.
